\text{CSAD}(\cos \theta^*, \phi^*)^{\text{MC}}_{\text{pre-FSR}} = \sum_{i=0}^8 P_i^{\text{ref}} f_i(\theta^*, \phi^*)^{\text{MC}}_{\text{pre-FSR}}
